{{vgname|Granny}}是由{{lang|en|DVloper}}開發和發行的[[獨立遊戲|獨立]][[生存恐怖游戏|生存恐怖]][[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]，為《[[蘭德里納河|蘭德里納河]]》（{{lang|en|''Slendrina''}}）系列的衍生作。該遊戲含有解謎的要素，玩家控制著一個未知名的角色，必須在五天內利用線索解決難題，才能從一個充滿陷阱的房子中逃脫，否則就會被恐怖奶奶「解決」，同時避免還得遭受「恐怖奶奶（{{lang|en|Granny}}）」的一擊斃命<ref name="Tecnoblog(2020-06-17)">{{cite web|url=https://tecnoblog.net/346082/como-bugar-a-granny-e-conseguir-sair-de-casa/|title=Como bugar a Granny e conseguir sair de casa|last=Leonardo|first=André|work=Tecnoblog|date=2020-06-17|accessdate=2020-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720085244/https://tecnoblog.net/346082/como-bugar-a-granny-e-conseguir-sair-de-casa/|archive-date=2020-07-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在故事設定中，《蘭德里納河》的女鬼{{lang|en|Slendrina}}是恐怖奶奶的孫女<ref name="Tecnoblog(2020-06-17)" />。

該遊戲於2017年11月24日在[[Android|Android]]平台上首度推出，供大眾免費遊玩，並獲得了極大的關注<ref name="Newsweek(2018-03-23)">{{cite news|url=https://www.newsweek.com/granny-horror-game-walkthrough-cheats-rooms-items-ios-android-859002|title='Granny' Horror Game Walkthrough: Cheat List for Every Room Including Hidden Weapon Passage|last=Harbison|first=Cammy|work=[[新聞週刊|Newsweek]]|date=2018-03-23|accessdate=2020-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190704231633/https://www.newsweek.com/granny-horror-game-walkthrough-cheats-rooms-items-ios-android-859002|archive-date=2019-07-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>，下載量已超過了1億次<ref name="CyberScoop(2019-06-27)">{{cite news|url=https://www.cyberscoop.com/scary-granny-zomby-android-credential-stealing-wandera/|title=A zombie game with 50,000 Play Store downloads was pulling sensitive data from Gmail|last=Stone|first=Jeff|work=CyberScoop|date=2019-06-27|accessdate=2020-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200620065248/https://www.cyberscoop.com/scary-granny-zomby-android-credential-stealing-wandera/|archive-date=2020-06-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="HiTekno(2020-04-05)">{{cite web|url=https://www.hitekno.com/games/2020/04/05/084500/10-game-android-offline-terbaik-april-2020-auto-usir-kegabutan|title=10 Game Android Offline Terbaik April 2020, Auto Usir Kegabutan!|last1=Pratnyawan|first1=Agung|last2=Rachmanta|first2=Rezza Dwi|work=HiTekno|date=2020-04-05|accessdate=2020-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200410070538/https://www.hitekno.com/games/2020/04/05/084500/10-game-android-offline-terbaik-april-2020-auto-usir-kegabutan|archive-date=2020-04-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。續作《{{lang|en|Granny: Chapter Two}}》於2019年9月6日推出<ref name="HiTekno(2020-04-05)" />，Granny和Grandpa將同時追逐玩家，續作《Granny 3》於2021年6月3日推出，Granny、Grandpa和Slendrina將同時追逐玩家，使遊戲變得更加困難。

